  "title": "Assistant Vice President, Global Markets Operation Group - Derivatives",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Manage and support the overall operations such as but not limited to derivatives processing, confirmation and fund settlement, and effective control of the group related transactions.</li>\n  <li>Lead the derivatives team.</li>\n  <li>Investigate and report discrepancies and irregularities arising from transactions and resolve issues including handling stakeholder’s complaints and escalating all issues promptly.</li>\n  <li>Introduce effective risk management control features and policies to minimize errors and clerical mistakes taking in consideration our Bank’s policies and procedures.</li>\n  <li>Assist Group Head and Deputy Head in manpower planning and staff development for the group including staff appraisals.</li>\n  <li>Ensure group operates in accordance with local laws and regulations, Head Office policies and branch procedures.</li>\n  <li>Govern and control activities offshored.</li>\n  <li>Ensure prompt submission of statistical reports to local management, Head Office, and MAS.</li>\n  <li>Take note of recommendations and/or comments made by MAS/External/Internal/Head Office auditors and make appropriate checks on implementations.</li>\n  <li>Ensure staff are well versed with BCP procedures and processes to participate in regular BCP drills.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Degree in Banking &amp; Finance or equivalent</li>\n  <li>More than 5 years relevant experience in derivatives processing, confirmation, and fund settlement, and 1-2 years of experience as a team lead.</li>\n  <li>Possess critical thinking skills, and able to link diverse information to build a full picture and spot inconsistencies.</li>\n  <li>Meticulous, attention to detail with a risk and control mindset.</li>\n  <li>Good oral &amp; written communication skills, and strong inter-personal skills</li>\n  <li>Reliable team lead and team player, who is able to work with a diverse group of people.</li>\n  <li>Keen and proactive learner.</li>\n  <li>Effective time management skills, ability to work under pressure and meet cut-off times.</li>\n</ul>",
